  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _header: Runner Visibility, Input & Stats
  _tooltip: 'A list of every NetworkRunner currently active.


    The visibilty
    can be toggled as well as whether or not that NetworkRunner provides input. 
    The stats of the NetworkRunner can also be activated.


    Note, sholding shift
    while clicking the visibility icon will turn off visibility for all NetworkRunners
    except the one clicked; this functionality also applies to input.'
  _button: {fileID: 705221228}
